{"tid":1507433,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"懇求各位煙剷手足, 夢遊時請注意!!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T03:37:01.000Z","uid":283970,"like":562,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"93319fcd437eda3e6a39a5e9ef4b862ef91e72aa","tid":1507433,"uid":283970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"小弟雖然係P牌, 但希望用你少少時間睇一睇<br />\n每次食煙果陣行返去後排一邊, 面向牆壁, 飲水食野一次過做哂<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同埋有樣野好重要</span></span></strong><br />\n我知有D手足食開電子煙/IQOS果類, 其實呢類佔既比數唔多, <br />\n尤其IQOS有唔同顏色, 有D色係好少人用, 有時你地買埋唔同顏色既殼, 你一下子比人影到其實好易搵, 落到場希望你地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>粗粗地食返盒煙</strong></span></span>就算<br />\n<br />\n另外有時明白大家長期戴住mask好焗好辛苦, 抖氣果陣又係一樣, 注意周圍同最好搵後場地方隱閉既後巷休息, 有同伴既就搵同伴幫手留意前線環境, 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有樣野我想講<br />\n我知有前線手足D裝好靚, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">著到全身成個畜龍咁</span></strong></span>, 但唔少手足同我講, 退緊果陣見到你地跑緊, 好多手足以為係真畜龍, 有D手足想還拖果陣先發覺係手足, 我唔知你地應該點著, 希望你地諗諗計點樣唔好嚇到手足, 日頭都還好啊, 夜晚真係好難分架... <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割席<br />\n光復香港  時代革命<br />\n五大訴求  缺一不可<br />\n香港人 加油!!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d5ce15fdc5ed3897e161242aa8a694908bc51b3f","tid":1507433,"uid":33930,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:55:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=38e6752f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"a2721f3e976f19e394a743dccd57164b9490bd13","tid